---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Calculator Visualization - Free Online Calculators for Finance, Math, Fitness, Health"
>
  <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="ribbon ribbon-top bg-yellow">
        <!-- Download SVG icon from http://tabler-icons.io/i/star -->
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="icon"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke="currentColor"
          fill="none"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
            d="M12 17.75l-6.172 3.245l1.179 -6.873l-5 -4.867l6.9 -1l3.086 -6.253l3.086 6.253l6.9 1l-5 4.867l1.179 6.873z"
          ></path></svg
        >
      </div>

      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>About Us</h1>
          <p>
            Welcome to our calculator website! We're passionate about
            simplifying complex calculations and providing accurate results.
            Whether you're planning your finances, managing investments, or
            estimating loan payments, our user-friendly tools are here to assist
            you.
          </p>
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            Our mission is to empower individuals with the knowledge they need
            to make informed decisions. We believe that everyone deserves access
            to reliable financial tools, and that's why we've created a
            comprehensive collection of calculators.
          </p>
          <h2>What We Offer</h2>
          <p>
            Our suite of financial calculators covers a wide range of topics,
            including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Fixed Deposits (FDs): Calculate interest earned on fixed deposits
              based on different tenures and interest rates.
            </li>
            <li>
              Systematic Investment Plans (SIPs): Estimate returns on your
              mutual fund investments over time.
            </li>
            <li>
              Amortized Loan Calculators: Understand how your loan payments are
              distributed between principal and interest.
            </li>
            <li>
              Recurring Deposits (RDs): Plan your recurring deposit investments.
            </li>
            <li>Mortgage Loans: Determine monthly payments for home loans.</li>
            <li>
              Step-Up Calculators: Explore how your income can grow over time.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h2>User-Friendly Interface</h2>
          <p>
            We've designed our calculators to be intuitive and straightforward.
            No complex formulas or confusing jargonâ€”just input your data, and
            we'll handle the rest.
          </p>
          <h2>Accurate Results</h2>
          <p>
            Accuracy matters, especially when it comes to financial planning.
            Rest assured that our calculations are based on reliable formulas
            and up-to-date data.
          </p>
          <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
          <p>
            Behind the scenes, a dedicated team of developers, financial
            experts, and designers work tirelessly to improve our tools. We're
            committed to excellence and continuous improvement.
          </p>
          <h2>Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            Have questions, feedback, or suggestions? Reach out to us via our
            contact form, and we'll get back to you promptly.
          </p>
          <p>
            Thank you for choosing our calculator website. Let's simplify your
            financial journey together!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
